Menzies receives you with his characteristic mixture of charm and condescension.

"How can I help the Labor Party today?" he asks with a slight smirk.

What do you want to discuss?

- @menzies_communism: Anti-communism cooperation
- @menzies_constitutional: Constitutional matters
- @menzies_goodbye: End meeting

